Title: Einhell 4326141 TC-AP 650 E Reciprocating Saw 650W 240V EINTCAP650E
Description:
The Einhell TC-AP 650 E Reciprocating Saw is a compact and versatile tool which demonstrates its strong points on a wide spectrum of sawing jobs, particularly when rapid sawing progress is required. Its blade speed control electronics enables sensitive adjustment to the particular material, thickness and application.

The blade can be changed without the use of additional tools, saving time. The soleplate can also be adjusted without tools for optimum use of blade. It has a large, ergonomic handle with a soft grip area for increased comfort during work.

Supplied with 1 x Wood Blade.

Specifcations:

Input Power: 650W.
Strokes at No Load: 500-3,000/min.
Stroke Height: 20mm.
Capacity: Wood 150mm, Steel: 10mm.
Weight: 2.8kg.
